00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:23,868
or the browser as a platform.

402
00:14:23,868 --> 00:14:27,200
So to do that, we wrote
a library called ForPlay.

403
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,534
ForPlay is an abstraction layer
