00:16:21,834 --> 00:16:23,834
We have the game loop,
the I/O system,

457
00:16:23,834 --> 00:16:25,367
and asset management.

458
00:16:25,367 --> 00:16:28,334
ForPlay provides
the abstractions for you

459
00:16:28,334 --> 00:16:31,167
and swaps in the appropriate,
